Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:45.75,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(246,0,246,130)\fs18\1a&H45&\4a&H2D&\4c&H0F0F0F&\shad1}临近海边  宁静的露天浴场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里还没去过天然的温泉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我只在电视节目里看过介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让身心都暖烘烘的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在下次放假的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那蓝华也能去啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不能去我也要去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 那就大家一起去温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去温泉要带什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈的话 不用你带也会一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和艾莉西亚前辈一起去温泉～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某人陷入妄想状态中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！赶紧结束练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟艾莉西亚前辈一起去温泉啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮递员先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的工作结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝吗？虽然可能有点不好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹的雪虫打扮得真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要去体验第一次的温泉之旅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天要是水道的水也像温泉一样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老伯伯 烟囱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各家各户都开始用壁炉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天的黄昏让人想家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 总觉得是个温暖的景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暖洋洋的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里也来织织看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能办得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 灯里的话一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力织出跟艾莉西亚前辈配对的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也给亚利亚社长织一套围巾和帽子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 首先棒针要这么拿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后像这样把毛线用食指勾住…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思 结果都是让蓝华去预约的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我刚好知道一个很棒的温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好期待哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经能看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,210)\fs34\frz6\c&HE0C8AA&\b1}土产
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这房间好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和期待的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们准备准备去泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是灯里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脱下来的衣服放在里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我第一次跟不认识的人一起泡大浴池…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 蓝华 我先进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我 等等我 等等我 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磨磨蹭蹭笨手笨脚 禁止…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路很滑 要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 很特别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这里原来只是一个古旧的大宅子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有这座宅邸的是一对很有情调的老夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说他们发现温泉以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆就把宅邸的一部分建成浴池了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建筑物本身虽然年久失修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这也别有一番风味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像传说故事中的精灵之家一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉还延伸到更深处…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 来这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉水好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗完澡果然还是要喝咖啡牛奶啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 很精通嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是正确的喝法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通体舒畅啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 舒服地泡完澡之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是令人期待的晚餐时间～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝佳的美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有冻死人的特训 暖洋洋的又悠闲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前不再是大嗓门的前辈 而是艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极乐啊极乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 表情太陶醉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级像换了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗？我这样很幸福 所以别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太舒服了 不小心就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是这种时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时的这时候 工作已经告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在准备晚餐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实在这样的假日里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个单手套领航员才该拼命练习才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像做了不该做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样行吗？这么悠闲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让你这么悠闲也是温泉的魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了度过寒冷漫长的冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是需要喘口气的时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 虽然我不习惯冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有可爱的雪虫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有令人想家的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有暖炉的话 好像也能变得喜欢冬天了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还泡了温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉 一定是AQUA的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送给我们的温暖的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要再去泡一次温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为人们说「温泉要泡三次」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边有一个秘密场地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级心惊肉跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…还没到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 和大海连在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 难道你来过这温泉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但是不好意思说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你太见外了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海和温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 灯里 没规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是 这么宽广却不游泳很浪费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒也是 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然冬天的空气很清新 星星看得很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像又想睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃子汽水 是这里的名产哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好像作梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饱喝足了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟您一起的客人已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晃前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没赶上晚餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我请她们来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气氛不太热烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要通宵好好享受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通宵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从极乐…堕入了地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一套！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再…出一身汗…才去温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华接下来是艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和你决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 我不想打了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪虫…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们为了过冬 要回到水曲柳上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？要道别了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 AQUA的雪虫非常长寿的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 到了明年的冬天一定还能见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新威尼斯有个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「雪虫踏上旅程的时候就会下起初雪」的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪会那么冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 AQUA的冬天确实很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也有很多美好的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以后每年都会期待着冬天的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和雪虫也会再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想来看看冬天的新威尼斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.21,0:24:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们总有一天会成为独当一面的领航员的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.84,0:24:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为一个独立的正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.15,0:24:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话…就…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.82,0:24:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些 橘色的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.07,0:24:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起度过美好的时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:54.98,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}風が凪いて 振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:02:04.24,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}夕映えに 照らされ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:13.92,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心までも 染まってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.64,0:02:24.96,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}見上げれば 響きだす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:32.94,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}星たちの歌が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:43.09,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 遥か未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:52.11,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水面に 夢 広がる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:03:06.66,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 見つけよう まだ知らない 宝物を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:12.93,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}あなたと一緒に 探そう
